<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Announcement Bar with Countdown Timer - Installation and Guide</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f6f9;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 110vh;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #333333; /* WhatsApp Green */
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 0;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: stretch;
            padding: 15px 20px;
        }

        header img {
            height: 45px;
            width: 45px;
        }

        .container {
            margin-top: -14em;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #666666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer p {
            color: #fff;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #666666;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            background-color: #333333; /* WhatsApp Green */
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: lightgray; /* Darker WhatsApp Green */
        }

        .cta-button:active {
            background-color: #25D366;
        }

        .footer {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #6d2727;
            background-color: #333333;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #f82424e8;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .guide-section {
            margin-left: 7%;
            width: 40%;
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .guide-section h2 {
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 1.7em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .guide-section ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        .guide-section li {
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <!-- Add Logo to the left of the header -->
        <img src="views/images/vid_logo-removebg-preview.png" alt="Logo" style="background-color: white; padding: 5px; border-radius: 5px;">

        <span>Buy Now Button</span>
    </header>
    
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to the Buy Now Button App!</h1>
        <p>Enhance your websiteâ€™s user experience by integrating a customizable announcement bar with a countdown timer to create urgency for your offers and promotions.</p>

        <!-- Install Button -->
        <button id="redirectButton" class="cta-button">Get Started</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Guide Section -->
    <div class="guide-section">
        <h2>How to Install and Use the Buy Now Button</h2>
        <p>Follow these steps to install and start using Buy Now Button on your website.</p>
        
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Step 1:</strong> Log in to your Shopify Admin Panel.</li>
            <li><strong>Step 2:</strong> Click the "Install Now" button above.</li>
            <li><strong>Step 3:</strong> Grant the required permissions.</li>
            <li><strong>Step 4:</strong> Access the Buy Now Button settings in Shopify.</li>
            <li><strong>Step 5:</strong> Customize the button placement and design.</li>
            <li><strong>Step 6:</strong> Save your settings and activate the button.</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>How the Buy Now Button Works:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>The Buy Now button allows customers to instantly purchase a product by adding it to the cart and redirecting them directly to the checkout page.</li>
            <li>This eliminates unnecessary steps, making the buying process fast, seamless, and efficient..</li>
            <li>It enhances conversion rates by reducing friction in the checkout process, leading to a higher likelihood of successful purchases.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Have questions? <a href="mailto:support@announcementbarapp.com">Contact us</a></p>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('redirectButton').addEventListener('click', function () {
            const shopName = "<%= shopName %>"; // Shopify Liquid variable to dynamically fetch shop name
            // Redirect to the authentication URL with the shop parameter
            window.location.href = `/auth?shop=${shopName}`; // Adjust the URL as per your app's requirements
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
